author: Simone Miranda
title: New Year’s Eve Wallpaper
text:
They say as you get older time goes much faster. I agree with that statement. Not that I’ll admit to being “older,” let’s just say I’m “wiser” than last year. 
Our designer, Jeff Maurer, reached into the far corners of his imagination and, inspired by the holiday’s festivities, he designed unique firework art … out of the words “Happy New Year!”
As you tip your hat at 2016 and turn to give 2017 a big welcome we hope you enjoy these typographic fireworks built just for you !
Be sure to check out the terms of use about using the wallpaper before you download it. Want to check out other designs? Visit our complete gallery of wallpapers here .
